{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5ebf1fb0db","title":"给周恩来等的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aeef3a0c62","index":0,"year":1958,"month":4,"day":25,"articleId":"5ebf1fb0db"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"69fcd7f9d3","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈云，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。德怀，即彭德怀，当时任中共中央政治局委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长。富春，即李富春，当时任中共中央政治局委员、国务院副总理兼国家计划委员会主任。一波，即薄一波，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、国务院副总理兼国家经济委员会主任。"},{"id":"7cfe39e0f0","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东这时在广州。"},{"id":"e116f7dd3b","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王鹤寿，当时任冶金工业部部长。彭涛，当时任化学工业部部长。滕代远，当时任铁道部部长。刘澜波，当时任水利电力部副部长。刘景范，当时任地质部副部长。李葆华，当时任水利电力部副部长。"},{"id":"f091beef73","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李锐，当时任水利电力部副部长、毛泽东的秘书。"},{"id":"c2028894b3","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"76051c5335","type":"title","text":"给周恩来等的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db"},{"id":"69fcd7f9d3","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来、陈云、德怀、富春、一波同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db"},{"id":"7cfe39e0f0","type":"paragraph","text":"想在这几天内谈一下工业问题，除富春已答应来此以外，你们几位是否有时间，是否愿意来此谈一下。如果可以来的话，请于廿五日或廿六日南来。又想邀王鹤寿，彭涛，滕代远，张霖之（煤炭部长），刘澜波，石油部长余秋里，地质部刘景范，水利部李葆华来此一谈，并请带季锐同志一道来。最好本（廿五日）日动身，以便开四天会，册日回去，五月一日站天安门。如何，请的复。或者今日到长沙，明日上午到此","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db"},{"id":"e116f7dd3b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db"},{"id":"f091beef73","type":"paragraph","text":"四月廿五日上午六时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db"},{"id":"c2028894b3","type":"paragraph","text":"刘邓即阅，用电话即发。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db"}],"page":{"id":"70d133f1f1","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"5ebf1fb0db","start":253,"end":254}}}},"__N_SSG":true}